    "body": "If you haven’t already, check out our [contributing guidelines](https://github.com/Expensify/ReactNativeChat/blob/main/contributingGuides/CONTRIBUTING.md) for onboarding and email contributors@expensify.com to request to join our Slack channel!\n___\n\n**Version Number:** 6.3.61-4\n**Reproducible in staging?:** Needs reproduction (Unable to reproduce)\n**Reproducible in production?:** Needs Reproduction\n**If this was caught during regression testing, add the test name, ID and link from BrowserStack:**\n**Email or phone of affected tester (no customers):**\n**Logs:** https://stackoverflow.com/c/expensify/questions/4856\n**Expensify/Expensify Issue URL:**\n**Issue reported by:** @rairibeiro\n**Slack conversation** (hyperlinked to channel name): [#Expensify Bugs](https://expensify.slack.com/archives/C049HHMV9SM/p1778078306821959)\n\n## Action Performed:\n\n1. Open Classic Expensify (iOS)\n2. Tap to capture a receipt using the in-app camera\n3. Bring the camera close to the receipt\n4. Observe focus behavior\n\n## Expected Result:\nCamera should:\nAuto-focus correctly at close range\nAllow clear capture of receipt text\n\n## Actual Result:\nCamera:\nDoes not focus when close to the receipt\nOnly focuses when moved farther away\nResult:\nReceipt appears smaller and less readable\n## Workaround:\nUnknown\n\n## Platforms:\nSelect the officially supported platforms where the issue was reproduced:\n- [ ] Android: App\n- [ ] Android: mWeb Chrome\n- [x] iOS: App\n- [ ] iOS: mWeb Safari\n- [ ] iOS: mWeb Chrome\n- [ ] Windows: Chrome\n- [ ] MacOS: Chrome / Safari\n\n## Screenshots/Videos\n\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/cef7f77c-cc80-4063-bbca-13e9f9f866e4\n\n[View all open jobs on GitHub](https://github.com/Expensify/App/issues?q=is%3Aopen+is%3Aissue+label%3A%22Help+Wanted%22)\n\n<details><summary>Upwork Automation - Do Not Edit</summary>\n    <ul>\n        <li>Upwork Job URL: https://www.upwork.com/jobs/~022052125853051425422</li>\n        <li>Upwork Job ID: 2052125853051425422</li>\n        <li>Last Price Increase: 2026-05-06</li>\n    </ul>\n</details>",
